text: Adi Nalić (born 1 December 1997) is a Swedish professional footballer. He is currently playing as a midfielder for Malmö FF. ==Personal life== Adi is the son of Bosnian professional football manager and former player Zlatan Nalić. Adi's grandfather, Mesud Nalić is also a former footballer, legend of Bosnian Premier League club Sloboda Tuzla. ==External links== * Malmö FF profile * * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish footballers Category:Mjällby AIF players Category:Landskrona BoIS players Category:Malmö FF players Category:Allsvenskan players Category:Association football midfielders
